# ZRent Platform — Flutter Architecture Plan

## Overview

Two Flutter mobile apps sharing a **single Supabase backend** via a common `shared` package structure within each app.

---

## Project Root Layout

```
s:\ZED\Zrent\
├── Agent Publisher-owner/     ← ZRent Agent App (Flutter)
├── User-Buyer/                ← ZRent Buyer App (Flutter)
└── packages/                  ← Shared Dart packages (optional mono-repo)
    └── zrent_core/            ← Shared models, services, constants
```

---

## Feature-First Architecture (Per App)

Each app follows **feature-first** with **4-layer architecture** per feature:

```
lib/
├── app.dart                   ← MaterialApp + GoRouter + Riverpod scope
├── main.dart                  ← Entry point
├── bootstrap.dart             ← Init Supabase, Firebase, env
│
├── core/                      ← App-wide infrastructure
│   ├── constants/             ← App constants, enums, keys
│   ├── errors/                ← Failures, exceptions
│   ├── extensions/            ← Dart extensions
│   ├── network/               ← Dio client, interceptors
│   ├── providers/             ← Global Riverpod providers
│   ├── router/                ← GoRouter config + route names
│   ├── theme/                 ← ThemeData, colors, typography
│   └── utils/                 ← Formatters, validators, helpers
│
├── config/                    ← Environment & 3rd party config
│   ├── env.dart               ← Env variables
│   ├── supabase_config.dart   ← Supabase init
│   ├── firebase_config.dart   ← FCM init
│   └── stripe_config.dart     ← Payment config
│
├── shared/                    ← Cross-feature shared code
│   ├── models/                ← Shared Freezed models
│   ├── widgets/               ← Reusable UI components
│   ├── services/              ← Shared services (location, storage)
│   ├── providers/             ← Shared Riverpod providers
│   └── repositories/          ← Shared repository interfaces
│
└── features/                  ← Feature modules (see below)
    └── <feature_name>/
        ├── presentation/      ← Screens, widgets, providers
        │   ├── screens/
        │   ├── widgets/
        │   └── providers/
        ├── application/       ← Use cases, business logic
        │   └── usecases/
        ├── domain/            ← Entities, repo interfaces, models
        │   ├── entities/
        │   ├── models/
        │   └── repositories/
        └── data/              ← Supabase services, DTOs, repo impl
            ├── datasources/
            ├── dtos/
            └── repositories/
```

