## Agent App — Feature Modules

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| `auth` | Login, register, password reset, OTP |
| `dashboard` | Overview, stats, quick actions |
| `properties` | Publish, edit, manage listings |
| `wallet` | Balance, transaction history |
| `withdrawals` | Request withdrawal, withdrawal history |
| `verification` | KYC, document upload, status |
| `messages` | Chat with buyers, media sharing |
| `notifications` | Push, in-app notification feed |
| `orders` | Incoming offers, transaction tracking |
| `analytics` | Property performance, views, leads |
| `subscription` | Tier management, upgrade, billing |
| `profile` | Agent profile, public profile preview |
| `settings` | App settings, account, privacy |

