## Core Layer Details

### Router (GoRouter)
- Route names as constants in `core/router/route_names.dart`
- Route config in `core/router/app_router.dart`
- Auth redirect guard in `core/router/guards/auth_guard.dart`
- Nested navigation for tabs (Buyer: home/discover/favorites/messages/profile)

### State Management (Riverpod)
- `@riverpod` code generation with `riverpod_generator`
- Feature-scoped providers in `features/<name>/presentation/providers/`
- Global providers in `core/providers/`
- Shared providers in `shared/providers/`

### Repository Pattern
- **Domain layer**: Abstract repository interfaces
- **Data layer**: Concrete implementations calling Supabase
- Riverpod providers expose repositories via `ref.watch()`

### Supabase Integration
- Auth → `supabase.auth`
- Database → `supabase.from('table')`
- Storage → `supabase.storage.from('bucket')`
- Realtime → `supabase.channel()` for messaging
- Edge Functions → `supabase.functions.invoke()`

---

## Shared Models (Freezed)

Key shared models across both apps:
- `UserModel` — Auth user profile
- `PropertyModel` — Property listing
- `PropertyMediaModel` — Images, videos, documents
- `MessageModel` — Chat message
- `OrderModel` — Transaction/order
- `EscrowModel` — Escrow state machine
- `WalletModel` — Agent wallet
- `ReviewModel` — Agent/property reviews
- `LocationModel` — Lat/lng, address, country
- `VerificationModel` — KYC/document status
- `SubscriptionModel` — Agent tier
- `NotificationModel` — Push/in-app notification
- `OfferModel` — Buyer offer on property

---

