# Utils
intl, url_launcher, share_plus, permission_handler
```

---

## Escrow State Machine

```
PENDING → FUNDS_HELD → INSPECTION → VERIFICATION → APPROVED → RELEASED
                                                  ↘ DISPUTED
                                      ↘ REFUNDED
```

